/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>2. The Luang Prabang Morning Market<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Directly after almsgiving, make your way to the morning market, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/Dku8fjPr2SC2XuLr7\" target=\"_blank\">located<\/a> next to the Royal Palace. Here you will find three streets filled with fresh vegetables, fruits, herbs and so on. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Must-read:&#xA0;<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/laos\/laos-travel-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Complete 10-day Laos Travel Itinerary<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120637\/market-luang-prabang-laos-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"market luang prabang laos\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"market luang prabang laos\" data-id=\"22948\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120637\/market-luang-prabang-laos.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=22948\" class=\"wp-image-22948 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120637\/market-luang-prabang-laos-540x