of Luang Prabang. It is a beautifully peaceful place to spend a few moments, due to its quiet location, tucked away down a side street. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/laos\/vang-vieng\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ultimate 3-day Guide to Vang Vieng &#x2013; 9 Things To do<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120559\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Wat-Pa-Phai.jpg\" alt=\"things to do luang prabang Wat Pa Phai\"><\/noscript><img width=\"382\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do luang prabang Wat Pa Phai\" class=\"wp-image-22969 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120559\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Wat-Pa-Phai.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120559\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Wat-Pa-Phai-300x265.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120559\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Wat-Pa-Phai-600x530.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120559\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Wat-Pa-Phai-679x600.jpg 679w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120559\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Wat-Pa-Phai-916x810.jpg 916w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04