\" height=\"300\" alt=\"things to do luang prabang Kuang Si Falls\" class=\"wp-image-22978 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls-1080x719.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls-1440x959.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120538\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-Kuang-Si-Falls.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4>Bear Rescue Center<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>At the exit of the waterfalls is the Tat Kuang Si Bear Rescue Center, which helps to rescue bears from the threat of poaching. <strong><em>However<\/em><\/strong>, the way they choose to treat, and display, the bears is not something that we support.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>One example of this is witnessing employees and tourists shouting at them to make them look into the cameras, or simply to get their attention. We understand a place like this supports the park financially, however, we can&#x2019;t support it.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Here are <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/sustainable-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">10 tips on how to travel more sustainably<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>7. Luang Prabang Night Market<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>After a day of exploring, the Luang Prabang Night Market is a great place to slow down. At sunset, Sisavangvong Road transforms into a charmingly lit, colorful street, filled with tents, selling different items. For example, clothing, wood carvings, jewelry, textiles, and various other knick-knacks. Because of the French influence, there are also numerous stands that sell delicious baked goods, and crepes!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120440\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-night-market.jpg\" alt=\"things to do luang prabang night market\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"307\" alt=\"things to do luang prabang night market\" class=\"wp-image-23168 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120440\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-night-market.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120440\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-night-market-300x204.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120440\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-night-market-600x409.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120440\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-night-market-800x545.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120440\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-night-market-1080x736.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120440\/things-to-do-luang-prabang-night-market-450x307.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinou