up\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Opening Times:<\/strong>&#xA0;The market takes place daily in the city center, from 5 PM &#x2013; 11 PM.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Also see: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/thailand\/best-market-bangkok\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">The best night market of Bangkok, Thailand<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>8. Street food market<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>On a side road, leading off from the main night market is an enormous street food market that you cannot miss. Countless stalls set up their seating in the narrow alley, selling coconut pancakes, rice\/meat\/fish skewers, fresh fruit shakes and so much more. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120428\/luang-prabang-guide-food-market.jpg\" alt=\"luang prabang guide food market\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"331\" alt=\"luang prabang guide food market\" class=\"wp-image-23173 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120428\/luang-prabang-guide-food-market.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120428\/luang-prabang-guide-food-market-300x221.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinour