<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There is a vegetarian buffet halfway along the street, that only costs 20.000 Kip (2.5 USD) for all you can eat! We were very grateful to be told about this by a Salt in our Hair reader (thanks again), as otherwise, we probably would have missed out on this fantastic thing to do in Luang Prabang!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120437\/asia-fish-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"23171\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120437\/asia-fish.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=23171\" class=\"wp-image-23171 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120437\/asia-fish-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120437\/asia-fish-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120437\/asia-fish-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120437\/asia-fish-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120437\/asia-fish-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120437\/asia-fish-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120437\/asia-fish-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120437\/asia-fish-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120437\/asia-fish-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-