wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"day3\">Day 3 &#x2013; Rivers and Mountain tops<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>9. Royal Palace, Luang Prabang<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Royal Palace in the center of town is absolutely beautiful. The open courtyard is free to enter, however, you will have to buy a ticket to enter one of the buildings. If you are interested in learning about Lao history, and culture, then check out the National Museum of Luang Prabang here.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/luang-prabang-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">See all hotels to stay in Luang Prabang<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120531\/luang-prabang-royal-palace-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"luang prabang royal palace\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"luang prabang royal palace\" data-id=\"22984\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120531\/luang-prabang-royal-palace.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=22984\" class=\"wp-image-22984 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120531\/luang-prabang-royal-