ason, the strong current, and high water levels of the river, wash away the bridge. In the dry months, it&#x2019;s worth seeing to catch a glimpse of the monks crossing the rickety bridge- a scene that makes you feel like you&#x2019;ve stepped back in time! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120503\/bamboo-bridge-river-luang-prabang-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"bamboo bridge river luang prabang\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"bamboo bridge river luang prabang\" data-id=\"23065\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120503\/bamboo-bridge-river-luang-prabang.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=23065\" class=\"wp-image-23065 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120503\/bamboo-bridge-river-luang-prabang-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120503\/bamboo-bridge-river-luang-prabang-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120503\/bamboo-bridge-river-luang-prabang-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120503\/bamboo-bridge-river-luang-prabang-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120503\/bamboo-bridge-river-luang-prabang-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120503\/bamboo-bridge-river-luang-prabang-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120503\/bamboo-bridge-river-luang-prabang-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-