s=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120450\/Mount-Phousi-luang-prabang-laos.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>At the start of the stairs, you will need to pay a small entrance fee. We advise against buying the birds that are being sold for good luck &#x2013; this is complete superstition and animal abuse.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121445\/sustainable-travel-cruelty-free.jpg\" alt=\"sustainable travel cruelty free\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"322\" alt=\"sustainable travel cruelty free\" class=\"wp-image-21452 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121445\/sustainable-travel-cruelty-free.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121445\/sustainable-travel-cruelty-free-300x215.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121445\/sustainable-travel-cruelty-free-600x429.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121445\/sustainable-travel-cruelty-free-800x573.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121445\/sustainable-travel-cruelty-free-1080x773.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121445\/sustainable-travel-cruelty-free-450x322.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121445\/sustainable-travel-cruelty-free-1536x1099.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121445\/sustainable-travel-cruelty-free-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/202