strong>Buses <\/strong>&#x2013;<strong> <\/strong>Buses from neighboring countries, like <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/thailand\/\" target=\"_blank\">Thailand<\/a> and <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/vietnam\/\" target=\"_blank\">Vietnam<\/a>, are available but will be long and tough rides.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/bus-vangvieng-luang-prabang\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Check for buses here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120418\/luang-prabang-bus-station.jpg\" alt=\"luang prabang bus station\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"luang prabang bus station\" class=\"wp-image-23178 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120418\/luang-prabang-bus-station.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120418\/luang-prabang-bus-station-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120418\/luang-prabang-bus-station-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120418\/luang-prabang-bus-station-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/202