tside of town.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Bicycle<\/strong> &#x2013; Rent a bicycle to get around town. Most hostels offer them but there are many rental shops in town as well. A good bicycle costs around 25.000 Kip (3 USD) per day.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Motorbike <\/strong>&#x2013; Rent a motorbike if you need to cover more distance. The roads around Luang Prabang and towards Kuang Si Waterfall are safe to drive. Expect to pay 80.000 Kip (9 USD) per day.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tuk-Tuk \/ Taxi<\/strong> &#x2013; Alternatively, pick a taxi or tuk-tuk if you want to reach areas that are further away.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120422\/taxi-laos-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"23175\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120422\/taxi-laos.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=23175\" class=\"wp-image-23175 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120422\/taxi-laos-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120422\/taxi-laos-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120422\/taxi-laos-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120422\/taxi-laos-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120422\/taxi-laos-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120422\/taxi-laos